<P><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">
With the second anniversery of EQ I thought a good poll to ask was just how many visitors here were playing on March 16th 1999, when the game was first released? So the new poll question will be "Where you playing EQ on the first day, 2 years ago?"
